WEBVTT

1
00:06:12.190 --> 00:06:14.340 
可当晚  有意思的事发生了
But a funny thing happened that night.

2
00:06:16.280 --> 00:06:18.540 
我没说他说是对的  可...
Look, I'm not saying he's right, but

3
00:06:18.540 --> 00:06:20.370 
巴尼的话的确有点道理
Barney does have a little bit of a point.

4
00:06:20.370 --> 00:06:22.000 
在这一点上  他可能说得道理
But on this one, he may have a point.

5
00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:22.960 
我是说
I mean, look...

6
00:06:22.960 --> 00:06:26.330 
重新协商感情中两人地位的想法
the idea of renegotiating the terms of the relationship,

7
00:06:26.330 --> 00:06:27.940 
是正确的
that's valid.

8
00:06:28.190 --> 00:06:29.350 
才不是
No.

9
00:06:29.350 --> 00:06:32.730 
你没有任何我想改变的地方
There isn't anything about you that I'd want to change.

10
00:06:33.230 --> 00:06:36.230 
或许是有那么一两个地方
Well, okay, maybe a couple of things.

11
00:06:36.230 --> 00:06:38.030 
比如什么
Like what?

12
00:06:38.030 --> 00:06:39.770 
就这样
And just like that...

13
00:06:40.090 --> 00:06:44.320 
这四对情侣中  有一对会在第二天分手
one of these four couples would break up the very next day.

